@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #000000
skinparam RectangleFontColor #000000
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7
skinparam noteBorderColor #000000

title Gateway Introspection Before Fix

rectangle "Athena Gateway\n/gateway/query" as GW
rectangle "Athena SDK query<T>()" as SDK
rectangle "Catalog Rows\nforeign_keys.source_columns = \"{user_id}\"" as ROWS
rectangle "PostgresCatalogSnapshotAssembler\n(addForeignKeyRows)" as ASM
rectangle "IntrospectionRelation\nsourceColumns: string" as REL
rectangle "Generator Renderer\nrelation.sourceColumns.map(...)" as RENDER

GW --> SDK : JSON response
SDK --> ROWS : data rows
ROWS --> ASM : raw row values
ASM --> REL : no normalization
REL --> RENDER : relation metadata
RENDER --> RENDER : TypeError\n"map is not a function"

note right of RENDER
Failure observed in `athena-js generate`
when FK arrays are serialized as strings.
end note

@enduml
